    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving pinnacle, featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with a blistering 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and engagement. The chassis benefits from a factory carbon fiber roof to reduce the polar moment of inertia and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adaptive suspension tuning. Maintenance is current, including the critical preventative replacement of rod bearings and throttle valve actuators. With its linear power delivery and stiffened subframes, this M3 offers the precise turn-in and tactile feedback expected of a well-maintained M-division icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
